.TH HELLO 1 "2026-06-12" "reprobuild" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hello \- print a friendly multi-output greeting
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hello
.SH DESCRIPTION
Demonstrates Recipe-Val M8 (Nix-style multi-output) under reprobuild.
The compiled binary ships under the package's
.B bin
output prefix; this man page ships under the
.B man
output prefix, content-addressed independently so a binary-only
consumer never pulls the man page into its closure.
.SH AUTHOR
Metacraft Labs.
